{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Strategize, overcome, and dominate your enemies, in this simple stylized game. Do you like turn based strategies but don't want to commit several hours to one game, this is the game for you! conquer your foe in 3 layered combat. utilize ground, sky, and underground to overwhelm your enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Trailer\u00a0Music by Kevin MacLeod</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is a turn based strategy that strives to have simple mechanics but complex strategy.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight on a 3 layered map, each layer with its own advantages and disadvantages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each unit has their own set of abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build defenses and traps to ward off attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock more units to gain a better advantage.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Controls</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">wasd- movement</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">left click- select</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">right click- pan camera</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">q/e- switch layer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">shift- move camera faster</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Map</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Ground Layer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/ground_layer.png?t=1739143344\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(Map defogged for display purposes)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is where most of the battle takes place. High ground is the advantage because units move slower up hill and get more movement range going down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Here is it with fog of war on</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/ground_layer_foged.png?t=1739143344\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Sky Layer</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/96cf526113c0df9a00907aec3d9be596_original.png?t=1739143344\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a high stakes, high reward layer where units move with great mobility attack power but there are also clouds that move each turn slowing or even stopping you from moving. sky superiority is a must if you want to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is how the clouds are at the start of the game<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/c7df4a6b8161188a0b0be9ae5b1f0044_original.png?t=1739143344\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">and this is how they are in the middle of the game<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/0333acf0e4660540d6daa5e7e5bce2a2_original.png?t=1739143344\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Underground Layer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/image.png?t=1739143344\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> This will be the layer where you can mine materials to boost your economy so you can unlock units more quickly. the fog on this layer returns at the end of each turn so be carful of ambushes. <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/486978aa48337b859e1491c03a49adf8_original.png?t=1739143344\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/ebafe6efffd87d236e0511b46af5784e_original.png?t=1739143344\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Current List of Units</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Cube Bot</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/b219402ad544870fbb63fa823546d269_original.png?t=1739143344\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The standard unit that's cheap and reliable.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Builder</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/fd0af327c28f565c65525f53e017580a_original.png?t=1739143344\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build walls for defense to impede enemy attacks. Will be able to build more on release.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Flyer</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/3f58a0d74c1c933202bba4196a4330a5_original.png?t=1739143344\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/773cbeb2f4a5030256f1e61defe9bacb_original.png?t=1739143344\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The flyer is the basic air unit that attacks other air units and can scout the ground with its scan ability. it spawns on the ground and flys up to the sky for the </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Miner</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/aada358a91b8609ce5d2c94497a9232e_original.png?t=1739143344\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The miner can place mines underground and above ground to make it more difficult for enemies to pass. Will be more useful on release when the underground rework is complete.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Tank</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/741ee7de3cdf88581c36bdcd87ecdc94_original.png?t=1739143344\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is the expensive tank. it has powerful ranged attacks and armor but moves slowly and has a tough time with going up hills.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Wall</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/0174c9c7264df59a4a752ca6e373ae0e_original.png?t=1739143344\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Despite its looks its a wall, it does what walls do. It's created by the builder. it's looks will be updated </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Mine</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/extras/5fafa7bbf2d5c897e8351704422a7112_original.png?t=1739143344\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It explodes. Its made by the miner</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739143344","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739143344","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/a9066d2133df242e6ef763d4ebc24a219a57226d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739143344","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349270/a9066d2133df242e6ef763d4ebc24a219a57226d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739143344","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3370740,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Strategize, overcome, and dominate your enemies, in this simple stylized game. Do you like turn based strategies but don't want to commit several hours to one game, this is the game for you! conquer your foe in 3 layered combat. utilize ground, sky, and und